   sustained declared period;
 - modeled fees and bonded value cover the security/availability budget with a
   frozen safety margin;
 - independent operators will supply the selected security, verification,
   availability, relay, or adjudication services;
 - exit, dispute, and failure paths work before mainnet or native-asset
   commitment.
 
 Nonclaims: compulsory settlement, token demand from L0 adoption, generic model-
 call currency, or one token per worker, GoalRun, room, node, or DAS.
 
 ## 8. Cross-Stage Work Packages
 
 These work packages do not create alternate dependency sequences. Each is
