 ### WP-RUNTIME — One governed execution fabric
 
 Stages: M0–M14, with selected-route terminality required by M9.
 
 Owner: canonical kernel master guide and migration matrix.
 
 Retained obligations:
 
 - one hashed registry classifies every externally reachable native and projected
   route, and one authoritative admission/final-invoker path governs equivalent
   native, MCP, client, and adapter calls;
 - classify `RuntimeKernelService` membership by required trust rather than
