 ### WP-PROOF — Portable evidence and compositional assurance
 
 Stages: M1–M14.
 
 Owners: daemon events/receipts, Agentgres, verification, assurance, wallet,
 storage, and domain owners.
 
 Retained obligations:
 
 - distinguish receipt, evidence, verification, acceptance, adjudication, and
   settlement;
 - protect exact bodies, refs, roots, signer/key/revocation inputs, checkpoint
