 The 2026-07-20 comparison against the locally inspected
 [OpenShip revision `081eb2057fc6`](https://github.com/oblien/openship/tree/081eb2057fc69b8c4b2782593ec3f7b9f3d2d294)
 is retained only as historical research provenance. Its useful pressure was
